 Technical Disclosure








www.ceterainvestmentservices.com does not currently collect personally identifying information about its users such as names, street addresses or e-mail addresses.For each visitor to www.ceterainvestmentservices.com, our Web servers automatically collect information about which pages are visited and the domain name (e.g., earthlink.com) of visitors. This information is used for internal review of website traffic.www.ceterainvestmentservices.com may place a "cookie" on the browser of a user’s computer. The cookie contains the stock and/or index symbols contained in the user’s watchlist. If you disable cookies on your computer, the watchlist feature will not operate properly.We do not control the policies of other sites to which we provide hyperlinks.





