Benefits




We get it. As much as you like your work, you need a competitive salary and benefits package that helps you make the most of your life and time spent outside the office.
401(k) – As a financial services firm, we understand the value of putting money aside for the future, so we help you save for retirement—with up to a 4% match to boot.

Generous PTO – We start you at four weeks per year, and it only goes up from there!
Health Insurance – You have a choice of plans to ensure you receive the best medical, dental, and vision coverage for you and your family for reasonable premiums.
Health Savings and Flexible Spending Accounts – If you have to drop the dough, it may as well be pre-tax; save money on healthcare, daycare, and more.
Disability Insurance – Life happens. We have both company paid short-term and long-term disability to pick you up while you are out.
Life Insurance – We hope you never need it, but we can help ensure your loved ones are taken care of should the unthinkable ever happen.






